{% comment %}
  == AI DOCUMENTATION ==

  ▸ PURPOSE
  Leaf block for rendering rich text content. Delegates rendering to
  snippets/text.liquid. Supports typography presets (rte, paragraph, h1-h6, custom)
  and full custom typography control when preset is "custom".

  ▸ CONTEXT
  - Parent: any container block or section that accepts @theme blocks
    (group, grid-row > _grid-column, carousel-block > _carousel-slide,
    hero-block, tab-content, generic-section, section.liquid, etc.)
  - Children: none (leaf block, tag: null)

  ▸ KEY SCHEMA SETTINGS
  - text (richtext): the content to display
  - type_preset (select): rte | paragraph | h1-h6 | custom
  - font (select): font family (visible when preset == custom)
  - font_size (select): size in rem (visible when preset == custom)
  - line_height (range 0.5-5, step 0.1): visible when preset == custom
  - letter_spacing (range -5 to 5, step 0.1, unit px): visible when preset == custom
  - case (select): none | uppercase (visible when preset == custom)
  - color (select): foreground | foreground-heading | primary
  - width (select): fit-content | 100%
  - alignment (text_alignment): visible when width == 100%
  - background (checkbox), background_color (color), corner_radius (range 0-50)
  - padding (4 range settings: block-start, block-end, inline-start, inline-end, 0-100px)

  ▸ USAGE EXAMPLES
  Template JSON — heading text inside a group:
    {
      "type": "text",
      "settings": {
        "text": "<h2>Shop Our Collections</h2>",
        "type_preset": "h2",
        "color": "var(--color-foreground-heading)",
        "width": "100%",
        "alignment": "center"
      }
    }

  Template JSON — custom styled label:
    {
      "type": "text",
      "settings": {
        "text": "<p>NEW ARRIVALS</p>",
        "type_preset": "custom",
        "font": "var(--font-subheading--family)",
        "font_size": "0.75rem",
        "letter_spacing": 2,
        "case": "uppercase",
        "color": "var(--color-primary)"
      }
    }
{% endcomment %}

{% render 'text', block: block %}

